FBIS3-56267 "drsov010_a_94013" FBIS-SOV-94-010 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Jan 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Reaction to Clinton Visit Mixed Zhirinovskiy on `Pointless' Visit LD1301155094 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1413 GMT 13 Jan 94 LD1301155094 Moscow INTERFAX Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Chairman of the Liberal Democratic Party Vladimir Zhirinovskiy believes that Bill Clinton's visit to Moscow is "pointless". Zhirinovskiy told journalists that the U.S. president had arrived in Russia "to support the government whose policies were not backed by the people during the elections on December 12." The day will come when America will appeal to Russia for help, he said.
